parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the Amazon QuickSight namespace that you want to describe.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The namespace that you want to describe.

nested_items.name: Namespace
nested_items.description: The information about the namespace that you're describing. The response includes the namespace ARN, name, Amazon Web Services Region, creation status, and identity store. DescribeNamespace also works for namespaces that are in the process of being created. For incomplete namespaces, this API operation lists the namespace error types and messages associated with the creation process.

nested_items.name: CapacityRegion
nested_items.description: The namespace Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: CreationStatus
nested_items.description: The creation status of a namespace that is not yet completely created.

nested_items.name: IdentityStore
nested_items.description: The identity store used for the namespace.

nested_items.name: NamespaceError
nested_items.description: An error that occurred when the namespace was created.

nested_items.name: IamIdentityCenterApplicationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the IAM Identity Center application.

nested_items.name: IamIdentityCenterInstanceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the IAM Identity Center instance.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
